that relates to the possibility of manufacturing life-saving medicines in space
with yields of 400 to 800 times the yields you can get on the ground. Now, what

08:58.220 --> 09:06.420
a great return that is to the taxpayer and to the well-being of our society out
of this new development in the NASA program.

