-pound box designed by McDonnell-Douglas Corporation to manufacture drug

12:24.380 --> 12:32.960
components in orbit for medical purposes. Both of these experiments were
originally scheduled for Discovery's first flight. The astronauts will also

12:32.960 --> 12:42.920
deploy several communications satellites. The crew on Discovery's maiden flight
will remain the same as was assigned to the 41D June mission. Later on this

12:42.920 --> 12:53.100
year, in another space shuttle mission, NASA may attempt to rescue two
satellites which were lost in space last February. We are optimistic about being

12:53.100 --> 13:02.220
